%   G e t L o c a l e L i s t                                                 %
%                                                                             %
%                                                                             %
%                                                                             %
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
%
%  GetLocaleList() returns any locale messages that match the specified
%  pattern.
%
%  The format of the GetLocaleList function is:
